\end_inset

core
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 of the global economy increasingly tenuous and uncertain.
 This motivated economic geographers to look for (and often claim they had
 discovered) the next new thing that could save homeland capitalism, and
 along with this economic geography went through a series of faddish 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

turns
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 (flexibility, cultural, relational, evolutionary, etc.).
 It became preoccupied with 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

the churn and chop of capitalist restructuring
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 but paid little or no attention to 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
