 with mainstream macroeconomics and its heterodox counterpoints, as well
 as enough mathematics both to make one's way through this often math-laden
 literature and to conduct independent research.
 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
after "490"
key "scott07economic"

\end_inset

